00:23:53.560 --> 00:23:55.120
Lord Rui Yu is actually a woman

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:24.000
Greetings, Your Majesty

00:24:34.840 --> 00:24:37.160
You handled border affairs as soon as you returned

00:24:38.400 --> 00:24:39.200
You have worked hard

00:24:40.600 --> 00:24:41.560
This is all

00:24:41.880 --> 00:24:42.920
my duty

00:24:43.800 --> 00:24:46.280
Pingxiang has sent envoys to negotiate peace

00:24:46.800 --> 00:24:47.960
They will arrive in the capital soon

00:24:49.000 --> 00:24:50.040
As for Qian Yuan

00:24:51.640 --> 00:24:52.960
Pan Zi Zhai colluded with Qian Yuan

00:24:53.000 --> 00:24:54.520
and disrupted the balance of the three states

00:24:55.280 --> 00:24:57.160
causing Ling An to lose good generals

00:24:58.960 --> 00:25:01.280
Qian Yuan wishes to downplay this matter

00:25:01.800 --> 00:25:03.560
Such wishful thinking is delusional

00:25:04.600 --> 00:25:05.080
Your Majesty

00:25:05.200 --> 00:25:06.920
I wish to send troops against Qian Yuan

00:25:07.360 --> 00:25:09.760
to honor the fallen and restore our prestige

00:25:12.200 --> 00:25:12.920
Your Majesty

00:25:13.680 --> 00:25:14.760
The war has just ended

00:25:15.320 --> 00:25:17.200
Countless people have lost their homes

00:25:17.760 --> 00:25:18.960
The borders need rebuilding

00:25:19.320 --> 00:25:20.920
We must not stir up trouble again

00:25:23.680 --> 00:25:24.960
As a general, Chenxiao

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:27.120
surely hopes the nation values martial strength

00:25:27.480 --> 00:25:28.880
and that generals can return to the battlefield

00:25:28.920 --> 00:25:30.040
to defend the borders

00:25:30.880 --> 00:25:33.440
but they do not wish for more wars

00:25:33.760 --> 00:25:35.360
that exhaust the people and drain resources

00:25:40.360 --> 00:25:42.800
Qian Yuan has demoted Pan Zi Zhai to commoner

00:25:43.360 --> 00:25:44.520
Spies from the Hidden Pavilion report

00:25:45.040 --> 00:25:46.560
Pan Zi Zhai cannot accept reality

00:25:46.560 --> 00:25:47.720
and has become deranged

00:25:48.280 --> 00:25:49.880
He has received his due retribution

00:25:50.440 --> 00:25:52.640
We should restore friendly relations

00:25:53.400 --> 00:25:54.480
and let the border cities

00:25:55.200 --> 00:25:56.760
have a chance to recover

00:26:00.560 --> 00:26:01.520
If so

00:26:02.640 --> 00:26:03.280
then I

00:26:03.480 --> 00:26:04.640
will show leniency

00:26:05.200 --> 00:26:06.280
and instruct Sifang Guest House

00:26:10.280 --> 00:26:12.440
to pardon Qian Yuan's offenses

00:26:12.760 --> 00:26:15.000
but postwar reparations must not be reduced

00:26:17.120 --> 00:26:17.760
Yes

00:26:19.960 --> 00:26:21.040
For your achievements this time

00:26:21.080 --> 00:26:22.080
at tomorrow's morning court

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:23.400
I will grant you a reward

00:26:24.840 --> 00:26:25.480
Your Majesty

00:26:27.640 --> 00:26:28.880
I have a matter

00:26:29.440 --> 00:26:30.760
to discuss with you

00:26:31.640 --> 00:26:32.360
Speak

00:26:34.960 --> 00:26:35.800
I

00:26:36.280 --> 00:26:37.800
wish to confess at tomorrow's court

00:26:39.000 --> 00:26:40.960
that I am, in fact, a woman

00:26:44.960 --> 00:26:47.360
You and Nan Chenxiao have achieved great merit

00:26:47.800 --> 00:26:49.680
and both have bright futures ahead

00:26:51.760 --> 00:26:53.680
Why do you suddenly wish to resign

00:26:55.840 --> 00:26:56.560
Chenxiao

00:26:56.800 --> 00:26:58.400
to quell the Pingxiang rebellion

00:26:58.960 --> 00:27:00.600
chose to resume his male identity

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:02.640
I, for the sake of our nations

00:27:02.840 --> 00:27:03.880
went to Qian Yuan as envoy

00:27:04.760 --> 00:27:05.840
and faced life and death

00:27:06.640 --> 00:27:09.400
which made me realize life is short

00:27:10.360 --> 00:27:12.200
winning someone's heart is truly rare

00:27:13.280 --> 00:27:13.920
Now

00:27:14.360 --> 00:27:15.720
the three states are at peace

00:27:15.960 --> 00:27:17.320
the people live in comfort

00:27:17.880 --> 00:27:19.160
civil and military relations are improving

00:27:19.720 --> 00:27:20.360
Everything

00:27:20.760 --> 00:27:22.560
is thriving and prosperous

00:27:24.040 --> 00:27:24.680
I

00:27:25.800 --> 00:27:27.200
wish to be myself again

00:27:28.280 --> 00:27:29.720
and live my own life

00:27:33.080 --> 00:27:34.320
If Ling An ever needs me

00:27:34.840 --> 00:27:36.520
even without the title of Lord Rui

00:27:37.080 --> 00:27:39.160
Rui Yu will still give my all

00:27:48.840 --> 00:27:51.840
You and Nan Chenxiao are my most trusted aides

00:28:01.080 --> 00:28:04.200
I do not wish to see such talent hidden away

00:28:11.400 --> 00:28:13.800
But I see your feelings for each other

00:28:15.520 --> 00:28:16.160
Enough

00:28:16.720 --> 00:28:17.280
I

00:28:17.480 --> 00:28:19.240
will help you fulfill your wishes

00:28:20.440 --> 00:28:22.120
Minister Liu is upright and honest

00:28:22.320 --> 00:28:23.480
He may succeed the position

00:28:24.200 --> 00:28:25.640
and continue to serve Your Majesty

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:28.840
To have such loyal ministers

00:28:29.440 --> 00:28:30.560
is my honor

00:28:31.840 --> 00:28:33.320
and Ling An's great fortune

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:35.840
Sixteen years

00:28:36.560 --> 00:28:37.840
have passed in the blink of an eye

00:28:39.800 --> 00:28:40.480
Lord Rui

00:28:41.200 --> 00:28:42.320
has accompanied Your Majesty

00:28:43.520 --> 00:28:44.640
all the way to this moment

00:29:18.680 --> 00:29:19.600
My lords,

00:29:20.000 --> 00:29:21.520
if you have something to say, speak plainly.

00:29:24.840 --> 00:29:25.440
Your Majesty,

00:29:25.880 --> 00:29:26.760
in my opinion,

00:29:27.160 --> 00:29:28.480
as Rui Yu's

00:29:28.680 --> 00:29:29.960
mentor,

00:29:30.080 --> 00:29:31.840
I wish to speak a fair word for her.

00:29:32.240 --> 00:29:33.440
Though she is a woman,

00:29:33.800 --> 00:29:34.560
yet

00:29:34.560 --> 00:29:35.880
she surpasses many men

00:29:36.040 --> 00:29:38.160
in wisdom and courage.

00:29:38.440 --> 00:29:40.720
In learning, she can debate scholars

00:29:40.840 --> 00:29:41.960
and turn the tide.

00:29:42.040 --> 00:29:42.880
In courage,

00:29:43.160 --> 00:29:44.920
she can enter enemy lines

00:29:44.960 --> 00:29:46.960
to buy time for our army

00:29:46.960 --> 00:29:48.320
and gather intelligence.

00:29:49.240 --> 00:29:49.880
Therefore,

00:29:50.480 --> 00:29:50.880
I

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:52.840
I earnestly ask you all

00:29:53.880 --> 00:29:55.640
to recognize Rui Yu's achievements.

00:30:03.960 --> 00:30:04.920
Your Majesty,

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:10.360
I know well

00:30:10.480 --> 00:30:12.840
that after revealing the truth, I should not remain at court.

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:14.840
I also beg Your Majesty

00:30:15.240 --> 00:30:16.760
to absolve the Rui family of guilt.

00:30:20.240 --> 00:30:21.400
Peace in the realm

00:30:22.480 --> 00:30:24.080
is partly thanks to you.

00:30:24.640 --> 00:30:26.320
How could I blame you?

00:30:27.480 --> 00:30:28.360
Since that is so,

00:30:29.440 --> 00:30:30.400
Rui Yu is hereby removed

00:30:30.840 --> 00:30:33.080
from the post of Second-Rank Scholar of the Hanlin Academy.

00:30:34.520 --> 00:30:35.840
Minister Liu will take the position.

00:30:38.560 --> 00:30:39.480
As a commoner,

00:30:41.040 --> 00:30:42.640
I thank Your Majesty for your grace.

00:30:47.400 --> 00:30:48.040
Rise.

00:31:05.920 --> 00:31:06.560
Master,

00:31:07.880 --> 00:31:08.400
Master,

00:31:08.480 --> 00:31:09.600
Lord Rui has returned!

00:31:10.360 --> 00:31:11.040
Good, good!

00:31:11.360 --> 00:31:12.120
Take me there.

00:31:12.240 --> 00:31:13.320
I want to greet them myself.

00:31:13.440 --> 00:31:14.000
Alright.

00:31:25.720 --> 00:31:26.320
Madam,

00:31:26.880 --> 00:31:27.720
what's wrong?

00:31:31.080 --> 00:31:32.560
I am Zi Zhai's aunt.

00:31:33.840 --> 00:31:34.480
Zi Zhai

00:31:34.640 --> 00:31:36.040
has committed such a grave crime.

00:31:36.520 --> 00:31:38.760
I truly don't know how to face you all now.

00:31:38.880 --> 00:31:39.480
Madam,

00:31:40.160 --> 00:31:41.320
you married into the Rui Residence,

00:31:41.640 --> 00:31:42.840
caring for everyone here.

00:31:43.080 --> 00:31:43.480
Father,

00:31:43.600 --> 00:31:44.440
Second and third brother,

00:31:44.600 --> 00:31:47.120
all praise your virtue and kindness.

00:31:48.040 --> 00:31:49.120
You joined our Rui family,

00:31:49.320 --> 00:31:50.560
so you are one of us now.

00:31:51.000 --> 00:31:53.400
You have no ties to those from Qian Yuan anymore.

00:31:54.480 --> 00:31:56.240
If there were any doubts about you,

00:31:56.400 --> 00:31:58.960
Father would not have told you Yu'er's true identity.

00:32:02.320 --> 00:32:03.120
By the way,

00:32:04.200 --> 00:32:05.360
speaking of little Yu,

00:32:05.600 --> 00:32:07.120
I'm still confused.

00:32:07.320 --> 00:32:08.480
They told me

00:32:09.000 --> 00:32:10.840
that little Yu is actually a girl.

00:32:11.200 --> 00:32:12.360
Before, they said

00:32:12.960 --> 00:32:13.240
that

00:32:13.960 --> 00:32:15.240
Chenxiao is a man.

00:32:15.400 --> 00:32:18.400
Why is your family so mixed up?

00:32:18.400 --> 00:32:20.320
The two of them are just

00:32:21.960 --> 00:32:23.360
swapped, aren't they?

00:32:23.680 --> 00:32:25.440
It doesn't really make a difference.

00:32:26.680 --> 00:32:27.480
Alright,

00:32:28.680 --> 00:32:29.400
from now on,

00:32:30.560 --> 00:32:32.000
let's just live well together.

00:32:53.200 --> 00:32:54.760
Now that the world is at peace,

00:32:55.120 --> 00:32:57.200
you no longer need to hide in the mountains.

00:32:58.200 --> 00:32:59.360
Go down,

00:32:59.560 --> 00:33:01.120
and return to your Jiangcheng Mansion.

00:33:02.960 --> 00:33:04.640
If Master hadn't saved us back then,

00:33:05.040 --> 00:33:06.120
we wouldn't have had the chance

00:33:06.200 --> 00:33:07.360
to see this prosperous age.

00:33:07.600 --> 00:33:08.560
Master's great kindness

00:33:09.080 --> 00:33:10.200
we disciples will never forget.

00:33:13.520 --> 00:33:16.040
I have taught you all my skills.

00:33:18.320 --> 00:33:19.120
Remember,

00:33:20.400 --> 00:33:22.880
after you leave, don't cause any trouble.

00:33:24.160 --> 00:33:25.920
I can't afford to lose face as your teacher.

00:33:28.800 --> 00:33:30.480
You must remember my teachings.

00:33:31.560 --> 00:33:32.960
Hold on to your original purpose.

00:33:33.200 --> 00:33:35.720
Be like your senior Nan Chenxiao,

00:33:37.480 --> 00:33:40.360
a good general who protects the nation and its people.

00:33:40.880 --> 00:33:41.840
Yes, Master.

00:33:45.680 --> 00:33:46.240
Master,

00:33:46.560 --> 00:33:47.320
take care.

00:33:51.880 --> 00:33:52.480
My lord,

00:33:53.280 --> 00:33:53.840
My lord,

00:33:54.120 --> 00:33:55.560
General Fu will return to the capital soon, right?

00:33:55.720 --> 00:33:56.600
Is everything arranged?

00:33:57.360 --> 00:33:59.960
Don't worry, General Nan has arranged everything for us.

00:34:00.120 --> 00:34:02.080
He even helped us get a house.

00:34:03.200 --> 00:34:04.760
Now that you've regained your status,

00:34:05.120 --> 00:34:06.520
you don't need to do this work anymore.

00:34:07.680 --> 00:34:08.520
It's fine.

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:10.480
I'll serve you a few more days.

00:34:10.680 --> 00:34:12.160
Once the young master recovers,

00:34:12.360 --> 00:34:13.600
and my family returns to the capital,

00:34:13.920 --> 00:34:14.720
then

00:34:14.840 --> 00:34:16.560
I can go home with peace of mind.

00:34:21.520 --> 00:34:22.360
What is this?

00:34:28.120 --> 00:34:29.840
The young master prepared this for you.

00:34:30.080 --> 00:34:32.240
He has been waiting for the day you regained your status.